datasets.name: dataset_4
queryLines: SELECT `Control` AS `Control`, DATE_TRUNC('DAY', `Event Date Time`) AS `Daily Event Date`, MEASURE(`Clicks`) AS `Total Clicks` FROM `workspace.default.hpx_events_model` WHERE `Control` NOT LIKE '%testid%' AND `Ui Action` = 'onpress' AND `Control` != 'welcome core navigationviewitem id' AND `Event Date Time` >= '2023-05-01' GROUP BY `Control`, DATE_TRUNC('DAY', `Event Date Time`) ORDER BY `Total Clicks` DESC LIMIT 10

frame.title: Top On Press Events by Control
